MORNING REPORT: MOVIES 
Rocky Mountain Film Fest: The Denver International Film Society has established 
the International Environmental Film Festival to showcase 30 to 50 top 
environmentally themed films and videos. The festival, which is set to run from 
March 13-17 in Boulder, Colo., is seeking film and video submissions from 
amateurs and professionals. The honorary board of directors includes Robert 
Redford, Jack Lemmon and Ted Danson. CLAUDIA PUIG 
